sudo mkdir /svnroot
sudo svnadmin create /svnroot/zhangban

sudo rm -rvf 目录
v :will display what you delete ，include the folder that you delete
r :指示rm将参数中列出的全部目录和子目录均递归地删除
f :ignore the file that not does not exit ,never give prompt

